title: Lek Shop Organic
description: Natural Thai health products, cosmetics, herbal products and herbal teas. Also serves herbal teas, high quality Taiwan teas, coffee, and vegan desserts, including cakes, chocolates, and ice-cream. Also offers vegan probiotic yogurts, set tea plates with fruit, juices and smoothies. Located on the same side as 7-11. Air-conditioned, free Wi-Fi.
